# Design System Tokens

**Figma source of truth:** [Foundations & Tokens](https://www.figma.com/design/AW4jk9SLPKlSqYt6NZ1QK5/Qure-%3C%3E-Figma-Design-system?node-id=9762-187&p=f&m=dev)

Variables and tokens below are derived from Figma node 9762:187 (Foundations). Use **only** these tokens in components. Do not invent values.

## Theming
- Light: `data-theme="light"` or no attribute on `<html>`
- Dark: `data-theme="dark"` on `<html>`
- Tokens switch by theme; never hardcode light/dark values in components.

