## Typography
- Font family: `IBM Plex Sans`
- Font sizes: 10, 12, 14, 16, 20, 24, 32, 40, 48, 64 (px)
- Weights: Thin, Light, Regular, Italic, Medium, Semibold, Bold
- Line heights: `--leading-tight` 16px, `--leading-snug` 22px, `--leading-normal` 24px, `--leading-relaxed` 26px
- Utility sizes: `--text-xs` 12px, `--text-sm` 14px, `--text-base` 16px, `--text-lg` 18px, `--text-xl` 20px
- Weights: `--font-regular` 400, `--font-medium` 500, `--font-semibold` 600

